by having fewer chin scales (5–7 vs. 8–10 in
H. huishuiensis
), more dorsal scale rows (24–27 vs. 13–15 in
H. huishuiensis
), and more ventral scale rows (13–15 vs. 7–9 in
H. huishuiensis
); from
